r_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a28aa076437afe04affd6d0acbeb4d6e?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a28aa076437afe04affd6d0acbeb4d6e?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1691065897, "last_modified": 1727059176}, "last_reply_by": "DiaoWang", "last_touched": 1727067968, "title": "24 岁，大专生，在亲戚公司工作 1 年半了，感觉生活没有未来，有什么人生建议吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1074980", "created": 1727059442, "deleted": 0, "content": "23 届毕业，22 年专升本失利，现在在函授\r\n\r\n现在亲戚一个月 5k ，打杂（负责员工上网管理，机器开机，科学上网），背着房贷，老登一起还（我 3k ，老登 4k ），每天不是上班就是下班睡觉，家里天天催相亲，楼主基本情况就这了，活着有点没意思了\r\n\r\n求指点，骂也可", "content_rendered": "<p>23 届毕业，22 年专升本失利，现在在函授</p>\n<p>现在亲戚一个月 5k ，打杂（负责员工上网管理，机器开机，科学上网），背着房贷，老登一起还（我 3k ，老登 4k ），每天不是上班就是下班睡觉，家里天天催相亲，楼主基本情况就这了，活着有点没意思了</p>\n<p>求指点，骂也可</p>\n", "last_modified": 1727059487, "replies": 60, "id": 1074980}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1700771269", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1700771269", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 64232, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1700771269", "stars": 9086, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 244127, "username": "Kung815", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Kung815", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8839/04bd/244127_mini.png?m=1634704585", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8839/04bd/244127_normal.png?m=1634704585", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8839/04bd/244127_large.png?m=1634704585", "created": 1500868455, "last_modified": 1634704585}, "last_reply_by": "lizy0329", "last_touched": 1727064886, "title": "游戏开发是不是众多工种中开发体验最好的？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1074815", "created": 1726993800, "deleted": 0, "content": "试看主流编程语言，Java 啰嗦冗长，Go 残缺简陋，C/C++年迈守旧，Python 性能拉垮，JS 生态混乱。而 Rust 、Kotlin 、Swift 等不成气候，不入主流之列。\r\n\r\n反观 C#，每每谈起，言者无不盛赞其设计之精妙，语法之贴心，加之背靠微软、游戏行业池大肉多，巨擘遍布，习此本领则不患糊口之难，后生涌入而僧多粥少之险。", "content_rendered": "<p>试看主流编程语言，Java 啰嗦冗长，Go 残缺简陋，C/C++年迈守旧，Python 性能拉垮，JS 生态混乱。而 Rust 、Kotlin 、Swift 等不成气候，不入主流之列。</p>\n<p>反观 C#，每每谈起，言者无不盛赞其设计之精妙，语法之贴心，加之背靠微软、游戏行业池大肉多，巨擘遍布，习此本领则不患糊口之难，后生涌入而僧多粥少之险。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1726993992, "replies": 57, "id": 1074815}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 223309, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4237, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 665942, "username": "huhu222", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/huhu222", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/daf81dd1986731b328ef99bfbe1ef742?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/daf81dd1986731b328ef99bfbe1ef742?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/daf81dd1986731b328ef99bfbe1ef742?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1701855283, "last_modified": 1701855283}, "last_reply_by": "flyingpige", "last_touched": 1727068014, "title": "理发怎么跟 tony 说啊, 每次都是剪短修一下, 但是每次效果不一样", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1074920", "created": 1727053477, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1727053477, "replies": 52, "id": 1074920}]